      "summary": "Following the natural way of cosmic order and harmony.",
      "category": "philosophical",
      "description": "Tao represents the natural order of the universe. Living in accordance with Tao brings harmony, while struggling against it creates suffering. Immortals achieve their state through following Tao.",
      "interpretation": "Fundamental principle of Chinese cosmology emphasizing natural flow and balance.",
